Dear Defender of the Fatherland! The Ministry of Defense of the Russian Federation asks you to come to the district military registration and enlistment office at the place of registration on February 22, 2222 for solemn congratulations on Defender of the Fatherland Day. Have a change of linen, personal hygiene products and a supply of food and water for three days with you. Sincerely, Minister of Defense RF S. K. SHOIGU